description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 songs, navigators, and avatars from J-POP, ANIME, VTuber!

Includes the navigator and avatar of the popular VTuber “HIMEHINA” !

This pack includes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
 - Indoor Kei Nara Trackmaker / Yunomi & nicamoq *Locked
 - I'm Getting on The Bus to The Other World, See ya! / Tuyu
 - Where Our Blue Is / Tatsuya Kitani
 - Show / Ado
 - The Brave / YOASOBI
 - Bling-Bang-Bang-Born / Creepy Nuts
 - Love Love Alien / Strawberry Prince
 - Stellar Stellar / Hoshimachi Suisei
 - Bishoujyo Muzai♡Pirates / Houshou Marine
 - Heart Pie Dancehall / HIMEHINA

■Navigator
 - Hime Tanaka(Heart Pie Dancehall) *with voice
 - Hina Suzuki(Heart Pie Dancehall) *with voice

■Avatar
 - HIME(Heart Pie Dancehall 1, 2D)
 - HINA(Heart Pie Dancehall 1, 2D)
 - HIME(Heart Pie Dancehall 2, 3D)
 - HINA(Heart Pie Dancehall 2, 3D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: Hit Song + VTuber Pack 6
